quests.desc: Welcome to TextWorld! First step, attempt to go south. That done, go to the west. Okay, and then, move north. And then, make an effort to go west. That done, go to the south. Once you get around to doing that, venture south. Then, attempt to venture east. Then, try to head east. With that accomplished, take the stick of butter from the board inside the dish-pit. Then, place the stick of butter on the floor of the dish-pit. Got that? Good!

objective: I hope you're ready to go into rooms and interact with objects, because you've just entered TextWorld! First of all, you could, like, move south. Once you get through with that, go to the west. Next, travel north. After that, go to the west. And then, make an attempt to go to the south. That done, make an attempt to venture south. Then, try to move east. After that, take a trip east. Then, take the stick of butter from the board inside the dish-pit. With the stick of butter, deposit the stick of butter on the floor of the dish-pit. And once you've done that, you win!
